Guard depends on blastcontain-core (Apache-2.0) for signing and the Charter
schema. It optionally exports decisions to OpenTelemetry and can back its
in-process enforcement with the Microsoft Agent Governance Toolkit (AGT) when
present — both via the availability-flag pattern (used-if-present, never
required); neither is vendored here. Record their provenance and licenses in
your own deployment's AIBOM.
